{"word":"ἐτεός","slug":"ἐτεός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n43109\" key=\"e)teo/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἐτεός</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ά</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">όν</itype> (not found in masc.), <sense id=\"n43109.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">true, genuine</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πόλλ᾽ ἐτεά</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:20:255\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">20.255</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἢ ἐτεὸν Κάλχας μαντεύεται</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:300\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.300</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εἰ ἐτεόν περ</foreign> whether it be <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">true</tr_> indeed, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:14:125\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.125</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εἰ δή ῥ᾽ ἐ. γε καὶ ἀτρεκέως ἀγορεύεις</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:15:53\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.53</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n43109.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐτεόν</foreign>, as <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adv.\">Adv.</a></pos>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">in truth, verily</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEI